name: dataverse app
description: This is a news publishing platform

streams.schema:
type blog @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: 0817f688-7428-46b4-9e83-2df50cf11658 | post") {
  author: DID! @documentAccount
  version: CommitID! @documentVersion
  title: String @string(maxLength: 100)
  content: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
}

type actionFile @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: 0817f688-7428-46b4-9e83-2df50cf11658 | ActionFile") {
  fsVersion: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  action: String! @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  relationId: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  fileName: String! @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  fileType: Int!
  accessControl: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  deleted: Boolean
  reserved: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}

type contentFolder @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: 0817f688-7428-46b4-9e83-2df50cf11658 | ContentFolder") {
  fsVersion: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  indexFolderId: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  mirrorFileIds: [String!] @list(minLength: 0, maxLength: 300000000) @string(maxLength: 2000)
  encryptedFileKeys: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  reserved: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}

type indexFile @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: 0817f688-7428-46b4-9e83-2df50cf11658 | IndexFile") {
  fsVersion: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  contentId: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  contentType: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  fileName: String! @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  fileType: Int!
  accessControl: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  deleted: Boolean
  reserved: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}

type indexFolder @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: 0817f688-7428-46b4-9e83-2df50cf11658 | IndexFolder") {
  fsVersion: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  folderName: String! @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  folderType: Int!
  contentFolderIds: [String!]! @list(minLength: 1, maxLength: 10000) @string(maxLength: 2000)
  accessControl: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  parentFolderId: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  childFolderIds: [String] @list(maxLength: 10000) @string(maxLength: 2000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  deleted: Boolean
  options: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  reserved: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}
